TPSA Shareholders Approve 800 Million-Zloty Buyback Plan

-- B y   M a c i e j   M a r t e w i c z
-- 
2011-10-13T11:34:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/tpsa-shareholders-approve-800-million-zloty-buyback-plan.html
Shareholders of  Telekomunikacja
Polska SA (TPS)  approved today a managemant’s plan, under which
 Poland ’s largest phone company, known as TPSA, will buy back as
much as 800 million zloty ($255 million) of its own shares by
the end of 2012.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maciej Martewicz at 
 mmartewicz@bloomberg.net  